    "body": "Yes, fast sync (default behavior) is causing this. Fast sync will download blocks and state concurrent. Once caught up geth will synchronize \"normal\".\r\n\r\n`--syncmode=full` will give you immediately the latest block but it will download the entire chain and execute all transaction.",
