    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "As Bas said, during fast sync, there's no full block yet (states are missing) and only the head block of the chain will be fully available. Hence during sync, the latest block will always be the genesis.\r\n\r\nYou can track sync progress via `eth.syncing`.",
